outputs.output_descr: Key ouput of SPDPC was (a) promotion of Millenium Development Goals through four seminars and one workshop;  (b) policy formulation related to foreign aids; (c) Donor database; (d) Papua need assessment; (e) Support peace and recovery process in Central Sulawesi; (f) An assessment of the socio-economic impact of the Bali Bombing; (g) the establishment and implementation of joint quarterly review metings for the CCF; (h) the formulation of project, "Information and Communication Technologies for Human Development", (i) the formulation of the "Asean-UNDP Partnership Facility" project.

project_descr: Support to Programme Development and Planning Coordination (SPDPC)
